Overview
========

This will be a collection of tools to help with time tracking.


timer
-----

The first utility is a simple timer.


tempus
------

The main program, incorporates the above timer and adds a logging ability.
You can set a name, project and sub-project and save and edit them.

They are saved to a SQLite database.


Building
========

Requires: sqlite3-devel, tokyocabinet-devel, gtk3-devel, glib2-devel


